high_descs: Move to stand on the side of the kitchen island closest to the window.
Pick up the sharp knife by the kettle from the island.
Carry the knife to the kitchen sink.
Use the knife to slice the potato in the sink.
Carry the knife to the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the knife in the top section.
Move back to the kitchen sink.
Pick up a slice of potato from the sink.
Carry the slice of potato to the microwave.
Place the potato slice in the microwave, turn it on, and then remove it once it's heated.
Carry the potato slice to the fridge.
Place the slice of potato in the fridge on the second shelf.
anns.task_desc: Move a heated slice of potato to the fridge.

high_descs: Turn right, go towards the oven, turn left after passing the kitchen island, go forward, turn left near the end of the kitchen island to face the island.
Take the large knife to the right of kettle on the counter.
Turn left, go forward to the sink.
Cut the potato in the sink into slices.
Turn right, go forward to the fridge.
Put the knife on the lowest shelf of the top compartment of the fridge.
Turn around, go back to the sink with the potato.
Take a slice of potato from the sink.
Turn left so the oven is to the right, go forward to the wall, turn left, go forward to the microwave.
Cook the potato in the microwave. Take the potato from the microwave.
Turn left, go forward, turn right at the fridge, go to the fridge.
Put the potato on the top shelf of the bottom compartment of the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked slice of potato in a fridge.

high_descs: Turn right and move to the other side off the island past the stove.
Pick up the knife next to the tea pot.
Turn left and move to the sink.
Slice up the potato that's in the sink.
Turn right and move to the fridge.
Put the knife on the top shelf in the fridge to the left of the potato.
Turn around and move back to the sink.
Pick up a slice of potato.
Turn around and move across the room to the microwave on your left.
Put the potato in the microwave on the plate. Cook the potato for a few seconds and then take it back out.
Turn left and move the fridge on your right.
Put the potato on the second shelf of the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked piece of potato in the fridge with the knife.
